data.description: Welcome Home! This remote mountain getaway offers ample privacy with 2.49 acres of mixed trees nestled in the tall pines of Section 31.  From the expansive front deck, enter this open floor plan home surrounded by picturesque windows, overflowing w/ natural light. The vaulted T&G ceilings, laminate wood flooring, gas fireplace and gas stove accent this two-bedroom two bath plus an add'l open loft/bedroom/den living space.  The outside brings the natural woods feel w/ the log façade exterior, metal roof, two car detached garage, workshop, 1000 gallon underground water storage tank and a 1500 above ground water storage tank. No HOA. Bring the toys, friends and family to escape the heat and start living!
